ns of the U.S. swim team.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"Murphy\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"a new level.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The Olympics\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"an all-consuming endeavor\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"several decorated veterans\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. swim team\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it seems to be having a therapeutic, grounding effect on them.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"effect\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a sport where years of grueling work can come down to margins smaller than the blink of an eye, perspective is a gift.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"grueling work\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"margins\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the blink\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"an eye\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"a gift\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cReally exciting to learn I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to be a girl dad,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Murphy said \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cJanuary of next year, my life is going to change a lot.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"a girl dad\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"Murphy\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u